notes: Overnight rain and winds had damaged parts of bowler's runup. Delayed start at 10:30 local time (08:30 GMT).
Match reduced to 45 overs-a-side. Field restrictions for the first 13 overs.
Strang not to bowl due to injury.
Brent and Huckle substitues for Goodwin and Strang.
ML Nkala took the wicket of SR Tendulkar with his second delivery in his first one-day international.
